hagbounce) statistic on Dyck paths, and our bistatistic\n(area,parabounce) on a sub-collection of those parallelogram polyominoes living\nin a (n+1)*n rectangle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Jul 2012 20:11:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 20 Jan 2013 10:13:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-22"}
