lations between spin-fluctuations\nand superconductivity may actually be quite widespread amongst the\nsuperconducting materials, and not necessarily be confined only to certain\nclasses of exotic compounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Aug 2012 12:03:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Aug 2013 08:26:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 27 Aug 2013 10:08:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-24"}
